snippet: Johnny Cueto threw his fourth complete game of the season and the Cincinnati Reds, aided by a bizarre play in which a Cleveland runner was fooled by a second ball on the field, defeated the Indians 9-2 on Tuesday night....

headline.print_headline: Bizarre Play, Cueto Help Reds Down Indians 9-2
headline.main: Bizarre Play, Cueto Help Reds Down Indians 9-2

lead_paragraph: Johnny Cueto threw his fourth complete game of the season and the Cincinnati Reds, aided by a bizarre play in which a Cleveland runner was fooled by a second ball on the field, defeated the Indians 9-2 on Tuesday night.
